### Gmail API Integration Module REST API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:2000

---
### 1. Initiate OAuth Login
### NOTE: Open this URL in your browser to actually authenticate and get the redirect to /callback.
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google


---
### 2. Fetch Latest 10 Emails
### Prerequisites: You must have completed Step 1 in your browser.
GET {{baseUrl}}/gmail/latest


---
### 3. Start Polling for New Emails
### Initiates background interval checking every 20s.
POST {{baseUrl}}/gmail/start-watch


---
### 4. Stop Polling
### Terminates background interval check.
POST {{baseUrl}}/gmail/stop-watch
